# timedNavigationMarkers

**Instance Property**

The array of timed navigation markers for which the group provides navigation.

## Declaration

```swift
var timedNavigationMarkers: [AVTimedMetadataGroup]? { get }
```

## Discussion

Returns the array of [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/AVFoundation/AVTimedMetadataGroup] objects managed by this group. This value may be `nil`.

## Inspecting Navigation Metadata

- **title**: The title of the marker group.
- **dateRangeNavigationMarkers**: The array of date range navigation markers for which the group provides navigation.
